org.teatrove.toolbox.beandoc
Class BeanDocDoclet

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.javadoc.Doclet
      org.teatrove.toolbox.beandoc.BeanDocDoclet

public class BeanDocDoclet
extends com.sun.javadoc.Doclet

The BeanDocDoclet generates "BeanInfo.java" files for each of the classes and interfaces to be documented. The Java file is created using an accompanying Tea template.

BeanDocDoclet makes use of the teadoc sub-package in order to wrap the classes of the doclet API to provide a Tea-friendly JavaBean interface for each class.

Author:
Mark Masse
